Package isocline.clockwork

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExecuteEventChecker
    Provides the function to check whether method is executed every time execution event occurs.
    FlowableWork
    It is an interface that enables flow control.
    ScheduleDescriptor
    An interface to implement the function to pass schedule setting status information to WorkScheduler
    Work
    An interface implemented by an object that defines the underlying operation.
    WorkEvent
    A interface that represents the event to be delivered when the work object is executed.
    WorkFlow
    Interface for work flow
    WorkSession
    Interface for Work session information

    WorkProcessor

    WorkSchedule
